02:04:41,058 --> 02:04:42,099
Very much.

1063
02:04:46,313 --> 02:04:48,981
- I have some news.
- News?

1064
02:04:51,818 --> 02:04:53,402
What, you're getting married?

1065
02:04:53,904 --> 02:04:55,071
I suppose.

1066
02:04:57,449 --> 02:04:59,992
I might be getting married
next spring, yeah.

1067
02:05:03,580 --> 02:05:05,247
You never said anything.

1068
02:05:07,376 --> 02:05:09,543
Been off and on for three years.

1069
02:05:13,590 --> 02:05:14,924
That's wonderful news.

1070
02:05:17,135 --> 02:05:18,260
Do you mind?

1071
02:05:25,602 --> 02:05:26,769
- Oliver.
- Oliver.

1072
02:05:26,853 --> 02:05:28,854
- Oliver.
- Hey, hey, hey.

1073
02:05:28,939 --> 02:05:30,231
Darling, when are you coming back?

1074
02:05:30,857 --> 02:05:32,149
I wish I was.

1075
02:05:32,484 --> 02:05:35,903
You caught us in the process of choosing
the new you for next summer.

1076
02:05:36,154 --> 02:05:38,656
- And guess what? He's a she.
- Oh, no.

1077
02:05:38,740 --> 02:05:41,450
Speaking of she's, I'm calling
to tell you guys I got engaged.

1078
02:05:43,412 --> 02:05:45,538
Wonderful!

1079
02:05:45,622 --> 02:05:47,498
- Congratulations.
- Mazel tov!

1080
02:05:47,582 --> 02:05:49,667
- Congratulations, Oliver.
- Thank you, thank you, thank you.

1081
02:05:49,751 --> 02:05:53,129
Listen, we'll leave you...
We'll let you speak to Elio.

1082
02:05:53,338 --> 02:05:55,423
- Happy Hanukkah!
- Happy Hanukkah!

1083
02:05:55,507 --> 02:05:56,632
Bye, sweetheart.

1084
02:06:04,391 --> 02:06:05,808
They know about us.

1085
02:06:07,269 --> 02:06:08,436
I figured.

1086
02:06:10,897 --> 02:06:12,148
How?

1087
02:06:13,900 --> 02:06:15,776
Well, from the way your dad spoke to me.

1088
02:06:17,195 --> 02:06:19,113
He made me feel
like I was a part of the family.

1089
02:06:19,698 --> 02:06:20,990
Almost like a son-in-law.

1090
02:06:23,201 --> 02:06:24,326
You're so lucky.

1091
02:06:25,912 --> 02:06:28,706
My father would have carted me off
to a correctional facility.

1092
02:06:31,251 --> 02:06:32,501
Elio.

1093
02:06:36,131 --> 02:06:40,176
Elio. Elio. Elio. Elio.
Elio. Elio. Elio. Elio.

1094
02:06:43,847 --> 02:06:45,347
Oliver.

1095
02:06:48,226 --> 02:06:49,769
I remember everything.

1096
02:10:54,639 --> 02:10:55,931
Elio.

1097
02:10:58,184 --> 02:10:59,184
Elio.

